    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I ran into the same error when creating a Proof-of-Concept gRPC application to see if gRPC would work for my use case. Basically I was trying to send 3 million simple messages from the server to the client, in a single stream, and as a result I get the OutOfDirectMemoryError. I am probably doing something wrong or gRPC was not meant for such use case. If anyone could help, that'd be great.\n\nThe code: https://github.com/lploom/grpc-OutOfDirectMemoryError\n"
