    "created_at": "2016-09-08T08:05:28Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-09-08T08:05:28Z",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I get one work around for this issue. reduce the times the rpc server send data to the client. Suppose you want to send 3 million records to client, you could reduce the time by create another message which hold \"repeated\" records of the send message. I do that by adding 10000 records to the new message and then do the sends. The error disappears.\nI think gRpc doesn't work well with millions records stream but by this way I could get it fixed.\n"
